Package simulation

package simulation
The Simulation package contains classes for simulating an ant colony optimization (ACO) algorithm on a graph. It includes the Simulation class, which manages the simulation process and events, and the InputParameters class, which holds the input parameters for the simulation. The package also includes classes for representing the graph, ants, pheromones, and other simulation entities.
  • Classes
    Class
    Description
    InputParameters
    The InputParameters class represents the input parameters for the simulation.
    Main
    The simulation.Main class is the entry point of the program.
    Simulation
    The Simulation class represents the simulation environment for the Ant Colony Optimization (ACO) algorithm.
